Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent

Class CheckboxServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>>

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent.CheckboxServiceFluent<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion.Insertion
public class CheckboxServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>> extends Object implements io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion.Insertion
Provides fluent methods for interacting with checkbox UI elements.

This class enables structured interactions with checkboxes, supporting actions such as selection, deselection, validation, and state retrieval. It integrates with CheckboxService to handle operations effectively and allows method chaining for better readability.

The generic type T represents the fluent UI service that extends UiServiceFluent, ensuring method chaining returns the correct instance type.
